The `snapshot_replay.condition()` function in R/snapshot.R handles how conditions are displayed in snapshots. When `cnd_class = TRUE`, it shows the condition class. The issue is that entraced base R errors now show `rlang_error` instead of `simpleError`. An entraced error from base R has an `$error` field containing the original error object. The fix requires checking for this field and extracting the original class.

